            <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion" data-animate="fade-up" data-animate-delay="100">
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-3 shadow-sm rounded-3" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
                <h3 class="accordion-header">
                  <button class="accordion-button rounded-3 fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="faq1">
                    <span itemprop="name">How do I get started with Launchpad?</span>
                  </button>
                </h3>
                <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                  <div class="accordion-body text-muted" itemprop="text">
                    Getting started is easy! Sign up for a free trial on our website - no credit card required. You'll have access to all features for 14 days. Our onboarding wizard will guide you through setting up your first project and inviting team members.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-3 shadow-sm rounded-3" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
                <h3 class="accordion-header">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed rounded-3 fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq2">
                    <span itemprop="name">What support options are available?</span>
                  </button>
                </h3>
                <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                  <div class="accordion-body text-muted" itemprop="text">
                    We offer multiple support channels: email support for all users with 24-hour response time, live chat for Pro and Enterprise plans, and dedicated account managers for Enterprise customers. We also have comprehensive documentation, video tutorials, and a community forum.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-3 shadow-sm rounded-3" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
                <h3 class="accordion-header">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed rounded-3 fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq3">
                    <span itemprop="name">Can I migrate from another project management tool?</span>
                  </button>
                </h3>
                <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                  <div class="accordion-body text-muted" itemprop="text">
                    Absolutely! We have built-in importers for popular tools like Jira, Asana, Trello, and Monday.com. Our migration specialists can also help with custom imports. Most migrations are completed within 24-48 hours with zero data loss.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-3 shadow-sm rounded-3" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
                <h3 class="accordion-header">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed rounded-3 fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq4">
                    <span itemprop="name">Is my data secure with Launchpad?</span>
                  </button>
                </h3>
                <div id="faq4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                  <div class="accordion-body text-muted" itemprop="text">
                    Security is our top priority. We're SOC 2 Type II certified, offer SSO and 2FA, encrypt all data at rest and in transit, and provide detailed audit logs. Our infrastructure runs on AWS with 99.99% uptime SLA. Enterprise customers can also request custom security reviews.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm rounded-3" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
                <h3 class="accordion-header">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed rounded-3 fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq5">
                    <span itemprop="name">Do you offer discounts for nonprofits or education?</span>
                  </button>
                </h3>
                <div id="faq5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                  <div class="accordion-body text-muted" itemprop="text">
                    Yes! We offer 50% off for verified nonprofits and educational institutions. Open source projects may also qualify for free or discounted plans. Contact our sales team with proof of status, and we'll set up your discounted account within 24 hours.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
